node.text:
Taking time to reflect on my actions and mindset is very important to me. I personally feel if I’m constantly doing things and don’t give myself a chance to reflect and think about where I’m headed, then really what am I working towards? I’ve had to be really honest with myself in the past and realize I was on the wrong path. It’s not easy realizing you’ve been holding yourself back, when you were blaming everyone else the whole time. But it’s possible to change. You have to want to be even greater. This version of me wasn’t built overnight; it took experience, pain, depression, and insecurities. I had to go through a lot to be where I am now. Be real with yourself and change for the better.
-
I wish you could see the @empirestatebldg in this picture, it was pink that night 💕
